Notes: Bates took the lead for good after trailing much of the game on a basket by
Goodridge w/9:52 to go, 39-37. That started an 18-8 run w/Yanofsky & Igoe each
scoring 8 for a 55-45 lead w/2:40 left. Wes got as close as 55-51 w/1:52 to go
Game.Officials: John Antolini,  Brian Alves,  Anthony Bagnoli
